title: Hey CNN, that’s NOT Eli Cummings; New Day deletes tweet with the wrong photo, is mocked hilariously
text:
Hey CNN, that’s NOT Eli Cummings; New Day deletes tweet with the wrong photo, is mocked hilariously Posted at 11:40 am on January 19, 2017 by Sam J. 
Look, Eli Cummings is pictured saying he’ll attend the inauguration … oh wait, silly CNN, that’s not Eli Cummings, that’s John Lewis. 
HA! 
— Cuffy (@CuffyMeh) January 19, 2017 
In case you didn’t know because you don’t watch or pay attention to CNN, New Day is an early morning show. 
Can you IMAGINE the screeching about this somehow being racist is Fox News had made this mistake? How black people don’t all look alike or something? Oh boy … gettin’ sloppy CNN, and we love it. . @CuffyMeh "I will also be attending the convention"– Marcellus Wallace pic.twitter.com/yL8oC7DQIA 
— Stephen Miller (@redsteeze) January 19, 2017 @redsteeze "Don't put that evil on me, Ricky Bobby!"
